---
title: Teriyaki Salmon Noodles with scallion and spicy chilli flakes
description: This heart-healthy pescatarian-friendly recipe is good for you but it's also filled with flavour. The perfectly pan-seared salmon matches amazingly with the tangy teriyaki sauce.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R12_W13_IE_IEXCQF0041-2_Main_high-6772a33f.jpg
